In November 2010 the UK government published a report on '''Low Carbon Construction''' containing an analysis of the Carbon footprint of the construction industry and a list of reccommendations for actions the UK government could take to reduce that Carbon footprint including proposals for changes to regulations and standards and government procurement requirements.

